1
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,880
I didn't expect that face of yours

2
00:00:56,119 --> 00:00:57,119
to be so effective.

3
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,119
For him,

4
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,960
it's likely a fatal weakness.

5
00:01:02,719 --> 00:01:03,920
Tonight, we

6
00:01:04,239 --> 00:01:06,040
made eight figures.

7
00:01:07,239 --> 00:01:09,599
But this is only the beginning.

8
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,599
Can I take over Lang Jiu's business now?

9
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,400
So impatient.

10
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,560
The final showdown hasn't even started yet.

11
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:51,879
When he's beaten down so hard he can't get up,

12
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,319
what I promised you,

13
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,000
I will arrange it.

14
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,199
Gentlemen, what is the meaning of this?

15
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,560
Winning and losing is part of the game.

16
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,759
Besides,

17
00:02:16,319 --> 00:02:17,680
isn't there still one round left?

18
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,240
The match isn't over yet.

19
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:20,800
Cut the crap.

20
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,280
Is this how you treat your guests?

21
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,680
Unlucky in the game,

22
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,400
but lucky in pleasure.

23
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:27,599
How could I let you gentlemen

24
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:28,919
go home disappointed?

25
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:32,120
Come in.

26
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,560
Gentlemen,

27
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:42,479
have some fun.

28
00:02:58,319 --> 00:02:58,840
Another round!

29
00:02:59,240 --> 00:02:59,840
Come on.

30
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,240
Where is Hei Ba?

31
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:06,520
Count off.

32
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:10,400
Eight-two-six-zero-eight-one.

33
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:11,960
You.

34
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,879
Eight-six-six-five-eight-eight.

35
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,120
Darn it! Do you want to die?

36
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,800
Please!

37
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,039
Let me go!

38
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,240
Let you go?

39
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:27,319
Now that you're here,

40
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:29,319
your life is no longer yours to control.

41
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,000
Listen up, all of you!

42
00:03:35,439 --> 00:03:36,599
You've come to Nine Heavens,

43
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,599
entered Liheng.

44
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,879
Whether you go to heaven or hell

45
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:43,039
depends on your own fate.

46
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,080
Smile and get in line!

47
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,319
Just like when you

48
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,560
were all smiling and begging me

49
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,199
to sign streamer contracts with you.

50
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,199
Once this is over,

51
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:55,120
every single one of you

52
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,599
will realize your greatest value.

53
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,560
Help!

54
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,560
Save us!

55
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:09,800
Help!

56
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,800
Scream all you want.

57
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:15,039
No one outside can hear you scream.

58
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:17,120
Save us!

59
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,800
Is anyone there?

60
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,279
Is anyone there?

61
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,720
Save us!

62
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,920
Let me go! Let me go!

63
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,319
Help!

64
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,120
Help!

65
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,279
Save me!

66
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:35,639
Is anyone there?

67
00:05:05,279 --> 00:05:06,199
Your face...

68
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,720
Does it hurt?

69
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,639
You're just here to play pool.

70
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,759
Everything else has nothing to do with you.

71
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:21,600
How did you...

72
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,519
Why are you here?

73
00:05:23,639 --> 00:05:24,879
Do you know what kind of setup this is?

74
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:25,879
And you dared to come up here alone?

75
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,720
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

76
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,439
Besides, my idol is here.

77
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,040
I have to protect him.

78
00:05:37,439 --> 00:05:39,160
Have you forgotten the lesson at the Abandoned building?

79
00:05:39,639 --> 00:05:41,000
You won't be that lucky every time.

80
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:42,639
Like I said...

81
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:44,399
You're on your own.

82
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,560
What's with that attitude?

83
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,279
Do you have any idea how dangerous it is here?

84
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:53,560
Why did you come here?

85
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:55,160
Who am I?

86
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:58,680
I'm a Popular Nine-ball streamer.

87
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,720
Sneaking into a place like this...

88
00:05:59,759 --> 00:06:01,120
...is a piece of cake for me.

89
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:03,279
You've got some nerve.

90
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,879
How dare you sneak out to the high seas alone to compete?

91
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,480
Aren't you afraid of being sold by Lang Jiu?

92
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,319
The grudge between us is already set.

93
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,879
I have to beat him this time.

94
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,279
I also discovered...

95
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:16,040
...this high seas tournament isn't that simple.

96
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:17,240
I just heard something.

97
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,360
Don't worry.

98
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:19,680
This time, I came...

99
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:20,959
...fully prepared.

100
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:22,480
Hello?

101
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,639
Don't worry.

102
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,079
They're all behaving.

103
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,399
The exchange at the pier is soon.

104
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:41,959
I can't believe they...

105
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,199
...are actually trafficking people.

106
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:46,920
It's absolutely insane.

107
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,680
We have to call the police and get them out.

108
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:54,600
Watch this.

109
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:19,920
The last batch of girls was top-notch.

110
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,040
Is this batch of goods ready?

111
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,680
Emergency tonight.

112
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:23,439
Deal canceled.

113
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:24,360
Do not contact for now.

114
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,959
If their ship goes back now...

115
00:07:30,959 --> 00:07:32,439
...they'll be caught red-handed at the port.

116
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:34,000
The rest is up to the police.

117
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,680
So that's it.

118
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:12,519
It actually helps me out.

119
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,840
The deal is canceled.

120
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:38,320
What should we do now?

121
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,320
What to do?

122
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,440
If you want to live...

123
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,240
...leave the rest to me.

124
00:08:51,679 --> 00:08:52,480
Don't get involved.

125
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:55,240
Aren't you one of them?

126
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,879
Why should we trust you?

127
00:08:58,399 --> 00:08:59,000
Have you forgotten?

128
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,360
I saved you once before.

129
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,320
So you can trust me.

130
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,679
Because I'm a woman too.

131
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,000
Boss Nan.

132
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:24,720
Boss Nan!

133
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,320
Why are you wailing this early in the morning?

134
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:30,279
Boss Nan...

135
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,279
B-B-Boss Nan...

136
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:37,120
Something happened.

137
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:37,879
The other side...

138
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:38,960
...canceled the deal.

139
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:40,360
The pickup ship suddenly turned around.

140
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,120
Since last night...

141
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,279
...we haven't been able to reach them.

142
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:44,360
This... this deal...

143
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,559
...is probably going down the drain.

144
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:50,480
You useless idiots can't do anything right!

145
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,279
Today's match...

146
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,720
...you must win it for me.

147
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:56,360
Get out!
